  "faqCategoryClasses": "Classes",
  "faqQ1": "How does QR check-in work?",
  "faqA1": "Each gym has its own QR. Open the Check-in tab, scan the code at the door, and wait for the confirmation screen. Your visit count updates instantly.",
  "faqQ2": "Can I switch tiers at any time?",
  "faqA2": "Yes. Upgrades are pro-rated and take effect immediately. Downgrades apply at the next billing cycle.",
  "faqQ3": "What happens if I miss a month?",
  "faqA3": "Unused visits don't roll over. Your visit count resets at the start of each billing cycle.",
  "faqQ5": "Which payment methods are accepted?",
  "faqA5": "Visa, Mastercard, CliQ, and Apple Pay. All billing is in JOD.",
  "faqQ6": "Can I freeze or cancel my subscription?",
  "faqA6": "There's no cancellation flow — you're not locked in. Your plan simply ends on the last day of your current term and you can choose to renew (or not) at any point. Freezing is available on 6- and 12-month plans: Silver gets 10/24 days, Gold 12/26, Platinum 14/28, Diamond 16/30 (6mo/12mo). The freeze is one block that can't be split; 12-month plans can freeze twice. Freeze shifts both your renewal and expiration by the days you actually use.",
  "faqQ7": "Is my data shared with gyms?",
  "faqA7": "Only what is needed for check-in: your name and tier. Your phone and email never leave our servers.",
  "faqQ8": "What's the difference between tiers?",
  "faqA8": "Every tier gives you 30 visits each month. What changes is the gym network you unlock — Silver covers entry-level gyms, Gold adds Silver + Gold, Platinum adds premium, and Diamond opens every partner gym in the network.",

